
("зилнзч"
 ((c-sf "фи") (relation absolute) (gv "MV") (c-root "зилнзч") (indir-obj -)
  ((dir-obj pers) 3) (reduplication -) (pv -) ((type root) null-root)
  (root "зилнзч")
  (or ((vv -) (tense {present imperfect conj-present}) (subj (f-subj))
       (dir-obj (f-obj)) (sf "фи") (voice medium) ((type subj3-sfx) "ш")
       ((type subj12-sfx) -))
      ((vv "п") (subj (f-subj)) (dir-obj (f-obj)) (voice {active medium})
       (or ((tense {aorist optative}) (passive-sfx -) ((type aorist-3sg) "з")
            ((type aorist) weak) (sf -))
           ((tense {future conditional conj-future}) (sf "ли"))))
      ((tense {pluperfect conj-perfect}) ((type aorist) weak)
       ((type aorist-3sg) "з") (voice {medium active}) (sf -) (subj (f-obj))
       (dir-obj (f-subj)))
      ((vv "ъ") (tense perfect) (sf -) (voice {medium active}) (subj (f-obj))
       (dir-obj (f-subj))))))

  (root "изсзуш")
  (or ((vv "з") (subj (f-subj)) (dir-obj (f-obj))
       (or ((tense {aorist optative}) (passive-sfx -) ((type aorist-3sg) "з")
            ((type aorist) weak) (sf -) (pv "кз"))
           ((tense {future conditional conj-future}) (sf "ли") (pv "кз"))

            ((type subj3-sfx) "ш") (sf "ли") (pv -))))

                       {"з" "зтф" "йз" "йзтф" "йзкз" "йзктф" "кз" "тп" "тф" "ъръ" "ял" "ялтф" "№з" "№зтф" "ѓзтф"}))))))))
